OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWindy at
OL,6,Ffirst, especially on coasts, but
OL,7,Feasing somewhat overnight. Dry with
OL,8,Fsunny spells for most parts this
OL,9,Fevening, then remaining dry overnight
OL,10,Fwith clear spells.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA dry day with plenty of
OL,13,Fsunny spells, and starting to feel
OL,14,Fwarm away from southern coastal strips
OL,15,Fwhere it may be breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
